&lt;p&gt;Harrogate is a high performing maternity unit and we are seeking highly motivated individuals to contribute and develop the delivery of high quality, evidence-based midwifery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have opportunities for enthusiastic and motivated midwives to join our well-established midwifery team. This is an exciting time as we shape the future of our Midwifery service and continue on a journey of improvement with our plans to implement the vision of Better Births (2016)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This post offers rotational opportunities throughout the maternity service, including in our Continuity of Care teams.&lt;/strong&gt; We actively support you to develop and enhance your skills in all aspects of midwifery. The successful candidate should have a good understanding of the national agenda within maternity and a clear commitment to helping the trust achieve this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in applying for the post we would welcome your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
